{"tid":1907063,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[外匯] 大戶價格陷阱實例 : EUR/JPY","createTime":"2020-03-02T10:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T08:11:44.000Z","uid":43407,"like":27,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4de6955e51e7b61a59f094e3845072aa505f1251","tid":1907063,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:58:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B6%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E5%AF%A6%E4%BE%8B-eurjpy/2583533211928607/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E7%259E%25AC%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258C%25AFk%25E6%2588%25BF%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%2599%25B7%25E9%2598%25B1%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E4%25BE%258B-eurjpy%2F2583533211928607%2F&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=bfbb420c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B6%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E5%AF%A6%E4%BE%8B-eurjpy/2583533211928607/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，沒見一段時間，希望各位都健康平安！<br />\n<br />\n之前我的貼文都主要是講解Order flow zone，今天我們溫故知新，一起再探討大戶的價格陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n小弟一向的主張，都是要知己知彼，目的都是跟隨大戶的足跡。要做到這一點，不單止要推測大戶的策略，還需要了解散戶的想法。散戶的行為模式，其實不是太難預測。我們一起看看以下歐元兌日圓的例子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPAaV8H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPAaV8H.png&h=d2038cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n散戶最常用去釐定市場方向的工具，都不離趨勢線或價格結構(Higher high/higher low 和 Lower high/lower low)。就如上圖歐元兌日圓的例子，我們可以見到上升趨勢線下破，在119.74創下了第一個lower low，之後價格回升至121.12後再度下跌，若果價格跌穿119.74的話，就形成了lower high和lower low，亦即代表下行趨勢確立，可以預料大量散戶會追沽。<br />\n<br />\n來到這一點，我們可以轉用大戶的角度去思考。若果他們想做空的話，那一個位置會是最理想，能夠提供最多的流動性(Liquidity)？在這一刻，市場上短線最多買單的位置，一定是在121.12之上，無論是突破做沽空，還是在最高點附近做空的交易者，都很可能會將止損，或心理止損移到121.12之上。因為他們都會認為，若升穿121.12的話，下行結構被破掉，價格應該會繼續向上，甚至重回上升趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n大戶看穿了散戶意料之中(predictable)的行事方式，待價格回調，並故意令它升穿121.12的位置，觸及散戶的止損單，或誘導他們自行平倉，這為大戶的空單提供了大量的對口供應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8qKf8R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8qKf8R.png&h=39d94b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n散戶眼睜睜的看著價格向下走，自己原本看對了方向，一毫也賺不到甚至虧損。市場就是這樣弱肉強食，要避免成為獵物，就要去了解大戶和散戶的想法和做事方式。其實也萬變不離其中，不是想像中那麼複雜。"},{"pid":"6d351785c5cf99645d34fcd064a1c4767c9ca1aa","tid":1907063,"uid":23269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:59:31.000Z","msg":"Lm 學野"},{"pid":"9052cd40fa580aa2596aa4b9e9928f8abca17918","tid":1907063,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T10:59:57.000Z","msg":"order flow點樣睇道指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f60c83655b0d20dbc4dd0ff0ca3a85a0f8732b1","tid":1907063,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:03:50.000Z","msg":"睇唔明"},{"pid":"6b915484e31abf60491734ca0086f480ad3e1ef8","tid":1907063,"uid":70892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"大戶做空咩意思"},{"pid":"711e5eace70adaee5b69bcfe1ef7ac23236b336c","tid":1907063,"uid":140450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b915484e31abf60491734ca0086f480ad3e1ef8","tid":1907063,"uid":70892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"大戶做空咩意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"有錢人沽"},{"pid":"ae011b41163330c1c68870047c6d6b5e1fec5556","tid":1907063,"uid":59376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:26:22.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\nChing 終於出文！"},{"pid":"6c1ae26201449399d965191dd94b6ca1092f6f1b","tid":1907063,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"我就係果個傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gi